Additional Information:
For example estimated timing of the Procedure.

This corresponds in eForms to BT-95 Recurrence Description.

(WG approval 2019-01-16)
 (epo:ProcurementObject) """@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "Has recurrence description"@en .

