epo:isJointProcurement a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:label "Is joint procurement"@en ;
    rdfs:comment """Multiple buyers procure together within the same procedure.

Addition Information:
In case the joint procurement involves buyers from different countries, the national law is specified by the epo:hasCrossBorderLaw in the ProcedureTerm .  (epo:Procedure) """@en ;
