    skos:prefLabel "Is joint procurement"@en .

epo:isListedCompany a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:label "Is listed company"@en ;
    rdfs:comment """Public companies listed on a stock exchange and subject to disclosure requirements (either by stock exchange
rules or through law or enforceable means), which impose requirements to ensure adequate transparency of 
beneficial ownership. 

<u>Additional Information:</u>

In eForms this indicator is used when the nationality of beneficial owner is not provided because the Economic Operator is registered in a regulated market that is subject to disclosure requirements consistent with Union law or subject to equivalent international standards which ensure adequate transparency of ownership information. 

WG Approval 21/11/2019 (epo:Business) """@en ;
    rdfs:domain epo:Business ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://data.europa.eu/a4g/ontology> ;
    rdfs:range xsd:boolean ;
